    "title": "Raspberries meadow - Vârtop trail",
    "description": "The unpaved road along the pasture lands, the sunset villages (Piatra Albă - Vârtop) and the raspberries meadow is pefect for an easy and relaxing bike ride. See here the trail and discover more hiking or bike trails from Rosia Montana. Book accommodation, bikes, guided tours, camping.",
